description: This easy-to-install wall light provides a very original way to decorate a child's room while providing comfort and reassurance during the day and the night. The light is easily placed in a beautiful setting of wall decals. An auto shut-off function is included, bringing the child 20-minutes of soft-glowing comfort while falling asleep. Just touch the light to turn it on. Low-Energy consuming LEDs assure that the 2aa batteries (not included) will last many months. Since the light is battery operated it does not require any cord making its placement easy. The lamp does not get warm to the touch making the product very safe for children and parents to use. There are several designs available making these wall decor lights suitable for many ages as well as boys and girls.
